Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.01,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051717,1053010}Now…{NOTE:さあ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:34.17,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053010,1054178}Y-Yes ma'am.{NOTE:は、はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.05,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054178,1056055}Ayuhara-san!{NOTE:鮎原さん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:39.01,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056055,1059016}Please promise me one thing.{NOTE:先生と一つだけ約束してちょうだい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.26,Default,Shimizu,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059016,1061269}That no matter what, you won't forget about volleyball.{NOTE:どんな時でもバレーだけは忘れないって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.39,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061269,1062395}I won't.{NOTE:分かりました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.77,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:1064021,1065773}– Let's go.\N– Okay.{NOTE:—行きましょう。\\N—うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.65,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:1066899,1068651}{\fad(700,300)}Ichinose's greengrocer{NOTE:野菜・果物\\Nイチノセ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068901,1070027}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.36,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070027,1071362}Ah, Kozue-kun.{NOTE:ああ、こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:53.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071362,1073906}How's your injury? Does it hurt?{NOTE:怪我は？怪我はどうだったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.03,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073906,1075032}Oh, this?{NOTE:ああ、これ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.40,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075032,1076409}It's nothing serious.{NOTE:大したことじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.40,0:17:58.66,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076409,1078661}Are you really okay?{NOTE:本当に大丈夫なの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:17:59.74,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078661,1079745}I am.{NOTE:大丈夫だよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.33,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079745,1081330}See?{NOTE:ほら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.96,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084709,1085960}I'm fine, really.{NOTE:本当に大丈夫なんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:09.58,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085960,1089589}The doctor said it's going to hurt for today,\Nbut I can go to work tomorrow.{NOTE:今日だけ痛いけど、明日はもう仕事に出かけられるって医者が言ったんだよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.13,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1089589,1093134}Tsutomu-kun, I'm begging you to stop this dangerous work.{NOTE:努くん、もうそんな危ないお仕事やめて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.13,0:18:13.84,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093134,1093843}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:17.05,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093843,1097054}I'll talk to my dad about you.{NOTE:私パパに努くんのことを話してみるわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:19.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097054,1099890}He'll definitely come up with a way to help you.{NOTE:きっと力になってくれると思うの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.51,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099890,1102518}Kozue-kun, that's the last thing I want.{NOTE:こずえくん、それだけはやめてほしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.89,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102518,1104895}I've bothered your dad too much already.{NOTE:君のパパには前にも迷惑をかけたし。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:27.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104895,1107607}I don't want him to help me again.{NOTE:又助けてもらうなんて僕は嫌だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.64,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107607,1108649}But…{NOTE:だって…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:31.19,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108649,1111193}Please understand, I have my pride as a man.{NOTE:とにかく、僕にも男の位置がある。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.57,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111193,1114572}I'm confident I can go through my problem alone.{NOTE:それに、今の不況乗り切って行く自信だってあるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.24,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114572,1116240}So please let me.{NOTE:だから邪魔しないでくれ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.78,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116240,1117783}Tsutomu-kun…{NOTE:努くん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117783,1120828}I understand, but I'm so worried about you…{NOTE:でも私努くんの事が心配で。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:48.66,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125625,1128669}Kozue-kun, you're of surprisingly weak heart.{NOTE:こずえくん。意外と気が小さいだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:52.38,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128669,1132381}I'm not going to stop with my direct sales, no matter what.{NOTE:だけど、僕は絶対に直売を止めないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.38,0:18:53.75,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132381,1133758}Kozue-kun, you see…{NOTE:僕はね、こずえくん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.75,0:18:57.72,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133758,1137720}I am not doing this just for money.{NOTE:何も金儲けのためにだけこんなことをしてるんじゃないんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:19:03.60,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137720,1143601}Have you seen how happy those housewives were when taking cheap and fresh vegetables?{NOTE:僕は安くて新鮮な野菜を持っていくことで団地の奥さん達はすごく喜んでくれてる。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.06,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143601,1145061}Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:07.77,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145061,1147772}I intend to put all I have into this work.{NOTE:僕はこの仕事に青春を懸けてるんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.48,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147772,1150483}That kind of trifle won't stop me.{NOTE:こんな怪我ぐらいでへこたれるはしないよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.44,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150483,1152443}I won't lose to you.{NOTE:お前なんかに負けるもんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:15.11,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152443,1155112}Tsutomu-kun, you've changed.{NOTE:努くん。あなたは変わったわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:18.11,Alternative,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155112,1158115}You've grown up so much more than me.{NOTE:私何かより(XX・大人に)なったみたい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.82,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158115,1160826}I have an idea. Let me help you around the store.{NOTE:そうだわ。この店を私にやらせてくれない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:22.07,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160826,1162078}Huh? You?{NOTE:え？き、君が？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:24.53,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162078,1164538}No way. You have your volleyball.{NOTE:だ、駄目だよ。君にはバレーがあるじゃないか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:25.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164538,1165748}Volleyball this, volleyball that.{NOTE:バレーはバレーだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165748,1168376}Even if you won't let me, I'll do it anyway.{NOTE:努くんがいけないと言っても、私は絶対にやるわよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:30.04,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168376,1170044}I've decided already.{NOTE:もう決めたんだから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.04,0:19:33.25,Default,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170044,1173255}B-But you have an important match in front of you…{NOTE:そ、そんな！だけど君には大事な試合が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:35.80,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173255,1175800}Promise me. Promise me, okay?{NOTE:約束よ。約束。いいわね？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.97,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183557,1185976}Professor Hongou. Professor Shimizu.{NOTE:本郷先生。清水先生。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.10,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185976,1187103}I'm sorry.{NOTE:ごめんなさい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:49.93,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188979,1189939}Ayuhara-kun!{NOTE:鮎原くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.48,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191899,1193484}Oh, Mitamura-kun.{NOTE:あら、三田村くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.98,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193484,1194985}If you're looking for Midori, she's inside.{NOTE:みどりだったら中よ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:56.65,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194985,1196654}No, I was looking for you.{NOTE:いいえ、君に用があってきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.65,0:19:57.90,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196654,1197905}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.40,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197905,1199407}I got this from Ichinose.{NOTE:これ一ノ瀬から。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:02.07,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199407,1202076}He asked me to deliver it to you.{NOTE:君に渡してくれて頼まれて持ってきたんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.74,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202076,1203744}Tsutomu-kun did?{NOTE:努くんから？}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.08,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207957,1209083}Dear Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.00,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209083,1212002}Promise me you don't get angry about what you're going to read.{NOTE:どうか僕の言うこと怒らないで聞いてほしい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:14.33,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212002,1214338}I thought about it a lot last night after our conversation.{NOTE:昨夜あれから僕は色々考えてみた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:18.71,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214338,1218718}I decided that I'll run my business alone.{NOTE:そしてやっぱり自分のことは自分でやるべきだと言う結論に達した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:23.05,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1218718,1223055}This means that I want to put all my energy into my work.{NOTE:つまり僕は自分の青春を力いっぱい自分の力で行きたいと思ったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.30,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223931,1226308}I thank you with all my heart for your friendship.{NOTE:君の友情には心から感謝するが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:29.81,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226308,1229812}But I'm not the man who ever gives up.{NOTE:…これくらいのことでへこたれる僕ではない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.81,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229812,1232815}I believe that you know it the best.{NOTE:それは君が一番よく知ってくれているはずだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:37.06,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232815,1237069}Please keep going on with volleyball\Nwith all you have.{NOTE:どうか君も君の青春を力いっぱいバレーにぶつけてくれたまえ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:42.65,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237069,1242658}Rather than pitying me, think of your own life.{NOTE:もし僕のことの同情する暇があったら……君自身の青春をもっと大事にするんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.65,0:20:45.03,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242658,1245035}Of your volleyball!{NOTE:君の青春であるバレーを！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:48.28,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245035,1248289}I find the way you are very beautiful.{NOTE:そんな君の姿は僕はとても美しいと思う。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:51.12,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248289,1251125}And I love you very much.{NOTE:そしてそんな君がとても好きなんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.79,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252460,1256797}I can't go cheer you on because of my work,\Nbut in my thoughts I will always be with you.{NOTE:仕事の都合で応援には行けないが、僕はいつも心の中で君を応援しているよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.34,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256797,1259341}Please make sure the double attack is a success.{NOTE:ダブル・アタックは必ず成功させてください。}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:01.34,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259341,1261343}Go! Go! Ayuhara!{NOTE:フレ！フレ！鮎原！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:04.97,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263721,1264972}Oh, Mitamura-kun.{NOTE:あら、三田村くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:06.68,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264972,1266682}K-Kozue, what's wrong?{NOTE:ん、こずえ、どうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:09.68,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266682,1269685}So Tsutomu-kun… where's Tsutomu-kun now?{NOTE:それで、努くんは…努くんはどうしたの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.39,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269685,1271395}Ichinose went to work.{NOTE:一ノ瀬は仕事に行ったよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.89,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271395,1273898}Huh? He left to sell again? That can not go well.{NOTE:え？仕事って直売の？行けない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:16.06,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273898,1276066}There's no telling what will happen to him this time.{NOTE:又努くんが今度はどんな目に会うか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.23,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276066,1277234}Hold on, Ayuhara-kun!{NOTE:待て、鮎原くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.02,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277234,1278027}Ah!{NOTE:あ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:18.98,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278027,1278986}Where are you going?{NOTE:どこへ行くつもりなんだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.53,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278986,1281530}Let me go! Let go of me!{NOTE:放して！放してよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:25.03,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281530,1285034}Kozue, are you going to skip the match with Misawa?{NOTE:こずえ、美沢との準決勝行かないつもり？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.03,0:21:26.41,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285034,1286410}Tsutomu-kun is in big trouble.{NOTE:努くんが大変なの。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.95,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286410,1287953}You have to play without me!{NOTE:試合にはきっと！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:29.20,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287953,1289205}Ayuhara-kun.{NOTE:鮎原くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.49,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289205,1291499}Don't you understand Ichinose's feelings?{NOTE:君には一ノ瀬の気持ちが分からないのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:37.92,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293751,1297922}Ichinose really wishes that you focus on volleyball.{NOTE:一ノ瀬は君がバレーに打ち込むことを心から願っているんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.34,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297922,1300341}That's precisely why he refused your love.{NOTE:だからこそ、君の恋を拒否した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:43.46,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300341,1303469}No, it's not just you. I was left behind too!{NOTE:いいえ、君ばかりじゃない。この僕だって断られたんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.46,0:21:44.72,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303469,1304720}Tsutomu-kun.{NOTE:努くん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.84,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307848,1308849}Kozue-kun.{NOTE:こずえくん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.84,0:21:50.39,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308849,1310392}And Mitamura.{NOTE:それから三田村。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.64,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310392,1312645}Let's spend our youth so that we have nothing to regret.{NOTE:お互いに悔いのない青春を送ろう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.23,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312645,1315231}To accomplish it, let's use all our strength sensibly.{NOTE:そのために若い力をぶつけて頑張るんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:57.94,Alternative,Ichinose,0,0,0,,{TIME:1315231,1317942}I'll work hard not to stand behind you.{NOTE:僕だって君たちで負けないで頑張るさ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:06.99,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1325658,1326992}Tsutomu-kun!{NOTE:努くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:08.82,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326992,1328828}Kozue, don't cry.{NOTE:こずえ、泣かないで。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:11.37,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328828,1331372}But… But Tsutomu-kun…!{NOTE:でも…でも努くんが…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:12.54,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331372,1332540}Tsutomu-kun…!{NOTE:努くんが…！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.04,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337002,1338045}Ayuhara-kun!{NOTE:鮎原くん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.04,0:22:19.58,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1338045,1339588}It isn't me who hit you just now.{NOTE:今殴ったのは僕じゃない。}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:20.96,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1339588,1340965}It was Ichinose!{NOTE:一ノ瀬が殴ったんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.96,0:22:21.79,Default,Ayuhara,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340965,1341799}Huh?{NOTE:え？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:26.09,Default,Mitamura,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341799,1346095}Are you… Are you going to trample on Ichinose's feelings and throw volleyball away?{NOTE:君は…君は一ノ瀬の気持ちを踏みにじってもバレーを捨てようって言うのか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.88,0:22:30.34,Default,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348889,1350349}Kozue…{NOTE:こずえ…}
